# 1. Basic macOS Runner Example

---

# Workflow

```yaml id="jlwm1y"
name: macOS Runner Demo

on: push

jobs:
  demo:
    runs-on: macos-latest

    steps:
      - name: Display Message
        run: echo "Hello from macOS Runner"
```

