# 15. Limitations of macOS Runners

| Limitation           | Description              |
| -------------------- | ------------------------ |
| Slower startup       | Compared to Ubuntu       |
| Higher cost          | macOS runners expensive  |
| Limited availability | Fewer concurrent runners |
| Long build times     | Xcode builds heavy       |

