# 16. macOS vs Ubuntu Runners

| Feature        | macOS          | Ubuntu          |
| -------------- | -------------- | --------------- |
| Best For       | iOS/macOS apps | DevOps/Web apps |
| Speed          | Slower         | Faster          |
| Xcode Support  | Yes            | No              |
| Cost           | Higher         | Lower           |
| Docker Support | Limited        | Excellent       |

