# 17. Best Practices

| Best Practice               | Reason                |
| --------------------------- | --------------------- |
| Use macOS only when needed  | Expensive runners     |
| Cache dependencies          | Faster builds         |
| Optimize Xcode builds       | Reduce execution time |
| Use matrix builds carefully | Avoid excessive costs |
| Store artifacts             | Preserve build files  |

