# 18. Common Mistakes

---

# Mistake 1 – Using Linux-Specific Packages

Some Linux packages unavailable in macOS.

---

# Mistake 2 – Ignoring Xcode Version Compatibility

Different iOS projects require specific Xcode versions.

---

# Mistake 3 – Large Build Times

iOS builds can become very slow.

---

# Mistake 4 – Assuming Persistent Storage

macOS runners are temporary.

